gradient-to-r from-white to-[#FFB347] bg-clip-text text-transparent\" href=\"/\">Dodo Academy</a><button class=\"md:hidden text-white focus:outline-none\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button><div class=\"hidden md:flex flex-col md:flex-row w-full md:w-auto gap-4 md:gap-6 items-center mt-4 md:mt-0\"><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition text-[#FFB347]\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition \" href=\"/critical/\">Critical Infrastructure</a><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition \" href=\"/foundation/\">Foundation Course</a><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition \" href=\"/consultancy/\">Consultancy</a><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=\"/login/\">Login</a><a class=\"bg-[#FFB347] text-[#0B1E33] px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#FFC97A] transition\" href=\"/register/\">Register</a></div></div></nav></header><main class=\"flex-grow max-w-7xl w-full mx-auto px-4 py-8\"><!--$--><div class=\"space-y-12 animate-fade-in\"><section class=\"text-center py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0B1E33]/5 to-[#FFB347]/10 rounded-3xl\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-[#0B1E33] mb-4\">Securing Nigeria&#x27;s<span class=\"text-[#FFB347]\"> Digital Future</span></h1><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8\">Empowering the next generation of cybersecurity defenders with world-class training and strategic consultancy for critical infrastructure protection.</p><div class=\"flex gap-4 justify-center\"><a class=\"btn-primary\" href=\"/foundation/\">Start Learning</a><a class=\"btn-outline\" href=\"/consultancy/\">Consultancy Services</a></div></section><section class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center\"><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#FFB347]\">500+</div><div class=\"text-gray-600\">Students Trained</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#FFB347]\">20+</div><div class=\"text-gray-600\">Expert Instructors</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#FFB347]\">15+</div><div class=\"text-gray-600\">Corporate Clients</div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#FFB347]\">98%</div><div class=\"text-gray-600\">Success Rate</div></div></section><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"card group\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🇳🇬</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#0B1E33] mb-3\">Protecting National Assets</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Specialised training for banking, power grid, telecommunications, and government network security professionals.</p></div><div class=\"card group\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🤝</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#0B1E33] mb-3\">Partnering with NSCDC</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Strategic collaboration with the Nigeria Security and Civil Defence Corps to strengthen national cyber defence capabilities.</p></div><div class=\"card group\"><div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🌍</div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-[#0B1E33] mb-3\">Global Frameworks</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">Training aligned with NIST Cybersecurity Framework, ISO 27001, and CIS Controls for global competitiveness.</p></div></div><section class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0B1E33] to-[#1A3A5F] text-white rounded-2xl p-8\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center\">Critical Infrastructure Protection Program</h2><p class=\"text-center mb-6 text-gray-200\">Designed for professionals securing Nigeria&#x27;s essential services</p><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">✓ Operational Technology (OT) Security</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">✓ SCADA and ICS Protection</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">✓ Incident Response for Critical Systems</li></ul><ul class=\"space-y-3\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">✓ Compliance (NIST, ISO 27001, NITDA)</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">✓ Hands-on Cyber Range Simulations</li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">✓ Nigerian Regulatory Frameworks</li></ul></div><div class=\"text-center mt-6\"><a class=\"btn-secondary inline-block\" href=\"/critical/\">Learn More About CIP</a></div></section><section class=\"text-center py-12\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-[#0B1E33] mb-4\">Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8\">Join Dodo Academy today and become a certified cybersecurity professional.</p><a class=\"btn-primary inline-block text-lg px-8 py-4\" href=\"/foundation/\">Enroll Now - ₦50,000 Only</a></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"bg-[#0B1E33] text-white/80 pt-12 pb-6 mt-auto\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3 relative pb-2 after:absolute after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:w-10 after:h-0.5 after:bg-[#FFB347]\">Dodo Academy</h4><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed\">Securing Nigeria&#x27;s digital future through world-class cybersecurity education and expert consultancy for critical infrastructure protection.</p></div><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3\">Quick Links</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=\"/critical/\">Critical Infrastructure</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=\"/foundation/\">Foundation Course</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=\"/consultancy/\">Consultancy</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-semibold text-lg mb-3\">Resources</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=\"/blog/\">Blog</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-[#FFB347] transition\" href=